{"tid":1161130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門威尼斯人外街頭廝殺 一死三傷","createTime":"2019-05-19T03:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T03:42:50.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7ade0cb16abc116c4c72c654af7b19efda45ee73","tid":1161130,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:04:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">威尼斯人天橋底發生懷疑斬人案<br />\n一男子傷重不治</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cms.exmoo.com/uploads/2019-05-18/rl1goz76n5ZES9jMYCaw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.exmoo.com%2Fuploads%2F2019-05-18%2Frl1goz76n5ZES9jMYCaw.jpg&h=0e2fd3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚約9時，金光大道澳門威尼斯人天橋底發生一宗傷人案，四名年齡介乎29至41歲的男子懷疑被人用刀斬傷。治安警察局表示，其中一名傷者經搶救無效死亡。<br />\n<br />\n據消防早前表示，死者胸部和兩邊腰部被刀刺傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"https://www.exmoo.com/article/107681.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.exmoo.com%2Farticle%2F107681.html&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPXlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=b89f5eb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.exmoo.com/article/107681.html</a>"},{"pid":"4cd1cba3c592b46d9c8c227ec485ca586c35504d","tid":1161130,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"據消防早前表示 ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b7c448321a3c49dce3fd13f3eedb0610fa9d39","tid":1161130,"uid":132128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"崩牙狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53921286a731705913e80304792194bd11cddef7","tid":1161130,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:25:42.000Z","msg":"真正嘅澳門終於返黎啦"},{"pid":"5be0323a474b05beba3573bbb1aa2e1395fd8f0c","tid":1161130,"uid":143